Walsh, Respondent, v. Mutual Life Ins. Co., Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. September 25, 1891.) Action by Patrick E. Walsh against the Mutual Life Insurance Company.

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon, J.

No opinion. Motion to go to court of appeals granted. For opinion on appeal, see 15 N. Y. Supp. 697.
